      <title>无人机袭击后维护工作导致俄罗斯炼油活动受到限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/russia-oil-refining-curbed-as-maintenance-follows-drone-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于刚刚从无人机袭击中恢复过来的炼油厂进入季节性维护，俄罗斯的石油加工率仍然面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/russia-oil-refining-curbed-as-maintenance-follows-drone-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 16:11:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对派称必和必拓南非公司拒绝对非国大的起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/bhp-s-south-africa-snub-an-indictment-of-anc-opposition-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[主要反对党表示，作为收购提案的一部分，必和必拓集团有限公司试图剥离英美资源集团在南非的资产，这表明执政的非洲人国民大会的经济政策如何削弱了投资者对该国的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/bhp-s-south-africa-snub-an-indictment-of-anc-opposition-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 16:11:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银分析师表示，英国工党可能会削减英国央行的银行存款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/ubs-says-investors-fear-labour-could-hit-uk-banks-boe-deposits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银分析师表示，投资者开始担心，未来的工党政府可能会通过减少商业银行在英格兰银行的存款赚取的金额来寻求为公共服务筹集资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/ubs-says-investors-fear-labour-could-hit-uk-banks-boe-deposits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 15:50:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登表示他将与霍华德·斯特恩坐下来辩论特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/biden-says-he-would-debate-trump-after-having-expressed-doubts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他打算在 11 月大选重赛前与唐纳德·特朗普进行辩论，这与之前表示不愿与前任同台演讲的言论不同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/biden-says-he-would-debate-trump-after-having-expressed-doubts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 15:26:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RedBird IMI 放弃电报投标，英国纸业待售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/redbird-imi-to-kick-off-sale-of-telegraph-after-uk-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，RedBird IMI 将放弃对《电讯报》的收购，此举可能会引发英国报业集团的另一场竞购战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/redbird-imi-to-kick-off-sale-of-telegraph-after-uk-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 14:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国到 2025 年将额外承担 80 亿欧元的净债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/germany-to-take-on-additional-8-billion-in-net-new-debt-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国联邦政府明年将拥有更多借贷余地，新债务净额将约为 240 亿欧元（合 258 亿美元），而不是财政部 7 月份预测的 160 亿欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/germany-to-take-on-additional-8-billion-in-net-new-debt-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 11:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
